classes, the order of appearance determines the cascade of the classes.</p>

<div class="example">

 <p>This example shows how to use the classes.</p>

 <pre>
 WEBVTT

 02:00.000 --> 02:05.000
 &lt;c.yellow.bg_blue>This is yellow text on a blue background&lt;/c>

